            <div>
                <head>Translated parts</head>
                <p xml:id="KR5c0386-start">
                    <seg corresp="#KR5c0386_tls_007-394a.2" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-08-11T03:59:32.58+09:00">he will both develop a disgraceful reputation</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5c0386_tls_007-394a.3" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-08-11T03:59:52.769+09:00">and become infamous for wanting to refor him [the heir to the throne].</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5c0386_tls_007-394a.4" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-08-11T04:00:03.964+09:00">He [the heir] will hate this attempt to prevail over him</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5c0386_tls_007-394a.5" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-08-11T04:00:14.48+09:00">and this will rashly provoke evil consequences.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5c0386_tls_007-394a.6" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-08-11T04:00:30.63+09:00">Therefore, he should behave stupidlyas if he were utterly in the dark,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5c0386_tls_007-394a.7" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-08-11T04:00:45.001+09:00">arcanely merging with both the brilliant and the dust,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5c0386_tls_007-394a.8" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-08-11T04:00:55.319+09:00">for only then could he manage to avoid appearing either intimate</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5c0386_tls_007-394a.9" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-08-11T04:01:13.492+09:00">or aloof</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5c0386_tls_007-394a.10" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-08-11T04:01:31.63+09:00">or appearing either beneicial</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5c0386_tls_007-394a.11" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-08-11T04:01:47.446+09:00">or harmful.</seg>
                </p>
            </div>
